{"tid":2304052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃之鋒：抗爭不會因被捕停止","createTime":"2020-11-28T12:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T13:26:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e0fe8ec1c5b97d3e39626e212eb1ada2d2c9e7f","tid":2304052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T12:25:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/7GMQGRY5YJCSLCJWYNH3LWM5SY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2F7GMQGRY5YJCSLCJWYNH3LWM5SY%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoRwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=f5b06589\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2F7GMQGRY5YJCSLCJWYNH3LWM5SY%2F&h=e29abd12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/7GMQGRY5YJCSLCJWYNH3LWM5SY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒：抗爭不會因被捕停止<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】早前承認煽惑及組織未經批准集結罪，正還柙候判的前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒，在獄中接受德國《世界報》的書面採訪，被單獨囚禁的他坦言想念家人，也害怕有朝一日會被國安法起訴，但相比起12名偷渡赴台途中被中國拘捕的香港人，他覺得自己的處境已是很好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/448lZK-hwi2SL34VngeKP89yuGo=/1398x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4KXC253FAJCQ7H2AZTEYEH2WBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F448lZK-hwi2SL34VngeKP89yuGo%3D%2F1398x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4KXC253FAJCQ7H2AZTEYEH2WBM.jpg&h=305027cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃之鋒在獄中接受《世界報》採訪，認為港人會變陣抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指其案件顯示港法律不公<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒冀外界別誤會，以為他、周庭和林朗彥等前香港眾志骨幹被捕，便是香港民主運動終結之時，他強調抗爭仍在進行中，因為這場運動由一開始便沒有大台，雖然每日都有抗爭者被捕、受審和入獄，武漢肺炎疫情也令示威的機會減少，但他認為港人會改用其他形式跟高壓政權周旋到底。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒指牢房的燈24小時長開，令他難以入睡。被問到是否覺得有公平審訊，黃之鋒回答對香港司法制度早已失去信心，他的案。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ad01b6684170f555212d63d3a6f86219058e9446","tid":2304052,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"在獄中都接受訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167f1ce832dfc366e0cd33beb1a7d5693c1390f4","tid":2304052,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"讚成！<br />\n<br />\n食緊黃店！<br />\n<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"91953f0a4c14d9831bf0655645b081aa2d936fd0","tid":2304052,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"167f1ce832dfc366e0cd33beb1a7d5693c1390f4","tid":2304052,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"讚成！<br />\n<br />\n食緊黃店！<br />\n<br />\n加油！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb1f3d463d96f30ef8e848849696f79ca882581","tid":2304052,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"df5d6a8e84219c959d9ab35498182ad828b912ff","tid":2304052,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:23:13.000Z","msg":"G Phone<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343150ebdba2df4c04ae6a56038c2e98357f2732","tid":2304052,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:25:08.000Z","msg":"支持拜登 個報應快到拜登未上台就坐監"},{"pid":"c8f66001f51c68b426ace6c0f2aa1c568bfb9373","tid":2304052,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"永遠支持你 gphone<br />\n仲咁勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}